414
00:25:54,240 --> 00:25:55,240
Sí.

415
00:26:01,235 --> 00:26:02,235
No.

416
00:26:03,160 --> 00:26:03,680
Señora.

417
00:26:04,000 --> 00:26:05,000
Gracias.

418
00:26:05,340 --> 00:26:06,340
Señora.

